{"tid":625450,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【特稿】古天奴仲有機會攞歐聯","createTime":"2018-04-11T12:53:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T13:02:31.000Z","uid":20634,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"30b0b988928bcdeae5a6b5b26ae02c82a8291518","tid":625450,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T12:53:27.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=60IjaljOmdVCL6an69oRXW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=1a1a7b88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】利物浦淘汰曼城闖入歐聯4強，而舊將菲臘比古天奴所屬的巴塞隆拿卻爆冷出局，不過原來後者也有取得冠軍獎牌的資格。<br />\n<br />\n根據歐聯規則，冠軍隊伍可以獲得40面獎牌，然後由球會決定由哪位球員獲分獎牌。如果利物浦最後贏得歐聯冠軍，今季曾經為紅軍上陣5場歐聯比賽的菲臘比古天奴（Philippe Coutinho），雖然已於1月轉投巴塞隆拿，卻因此仍有資格取得歐聯冠軍獎牌，但最後決定權仍落在利物浦手上。<br />\n<br />\n其實菲臘比古天奴離隊後，利物浦依然攻力驚人，更打破曼聯保持的歐聯單季入球紀錄。在8強次回合賽事，羅拔圖法明奴（Roberto Firmino）把握機會奠勝的入球，把紅軍今季在歐聯的入球數字增至33球，打破曼聯在2002/03賽季攻入32球的歐聯單季入球紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n利物浦之後還要面對歐聯4強的賽事，即至少多賽兩場，絕對有機會再度改寫這個紀錄。"},{"pid":"877f37d5f3efa48935a7ef564656922abd00a76d","tid":625450,"uid":9231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T12:54:56.000Z","msg":"古仔又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a34e5d1b5f26f91c80b5c8e2c981a053bf5e9cb","tid":625450,"uid":163842,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T12:56:05.000Z","msg":"如果可以，分埋比球帝好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"067fe6f83576ec2332bbef792ea1e61918c93641","tid":625450,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T12:56:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43485263da658feaaec1200e678229cf9d7138cd","tid":625450,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a34e5d1b5f26f91c80b5c8e2c981a053bf5e9cb","tid":625450,"uid":163842,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T12:56:05.000Z","msg":"如果可以，分埋比球帝好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T13:02:31.000Z","msg":"我地more than a club"}]}